<item>
            <title>[LU-11016]  PBS_JOBID value too large for JobID buffer (32)</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11016</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Getting error&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;May 10 16:55:31 r585i2n9 kernel: [1525996531.259303] LustreError: 16b-c: PBS_JOBID value too large &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; JobID buffer (32)
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The job id in this case was&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;3861053[112].pbspl1.nas.nasa.gov
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;#define LUSTRE_JOBID_SIZE 32
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;May be too small.&lt;/p&gt;

</description>
